Here's the optimized program:
```
int k;
int l;
volatile int m[5][8];
int fn3(int p1) {
  int o;
  for (;;) {
    for (; l; l--) {
      for (k = 0; k >= -27; k -= 6) {
        p1 = o - p1;
      }
    }
    p1 || m[2][5];
  }
}
int main() {}
```
